Maybe some of you will come at me for saying this, but both fandoms keep fighting between each other instead of spreading love for each other and be respectful,which is what our Idols really want

post: As a native Southern Californian, I know firsthand the devastation of wildfire across my home communities, and was particularly 💔 by the Australian bushfires. Australia has always given me so much love and support so FIGHT ON is one way to return that love, and help provide a little bit of joy to a country that’s given me so much joy. 🤗🤗🤗 Join me at Pioneer Park Recreation Reserve in Bright, VIC on March 11. Tickets to the concert are free and being distributed to emergency services who helped save lives and property as well as local residents from fire-affected communities. You can register for additional tickets at the link in my bio. Again, thank you to my Australian community for always being one of my biggest champions. I hope I can return the support to you ♥️ 🇦🇺
